snippet.title: Amber Howe
snippet.description:
Hey Babes,

My name is Amber and I make beauty & true crime videos. I like to chat about all things beauty related while also bringing you makeup tutorials and reviews of the latest beauty releases.  I also upload two true crime videos a week on a monday I have a series called missing mondays where I cover missing person cases. On a Tuesdays i have a series called true crime tuesdays where i cover a true crime case. I also upload fashion and lifestyle content from time to time.

I upload 5 times a week usually two true crime videos and three beauty related videos. 

Make sure you like comment & subscribe!

You can also find me here :

Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/amberhowexox/?hl=en
Twitter - https://twitter.com/AmberHowexox
Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/AmberHowexox/
Blog - www.amberhowe.co.uk


For Business enquiries please email:
amberhowebeauty@gmail.com
